					Create a file called run_thunderbird.sh and paste this in:
					code|
						#!/bin/bash
						# use -P profile name for profile
						xvfb-run thunderbird& 
						TB_PID=$!
						# wait 10 mins
						sleep 600
						kill -KILL  $TB_PID
						wait $TB_PID
						# leaves xvfb instance running but this will be reused by any later instances of xvfb-run
